  "title": "PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Apply hands-on expertise in the Singapore construction industry to execute and oversee project tasks effectively</li><li>Lead teams by communicating clearly with workers, supervisors, clients, users, and other stakeholders to align project goals and resolve issues</li><li>Monitor and report project progress and enforce quality control measures to ensure deliverables meet standards</li><li>Manage productivity by identifying and resolving technical issues to maintain workflow efficiency</li><li>Prepare and submit required documentation for authority approvals in compliance with regulations</li><li>Demonstrate responsibility and responsiveness by proactively seeking and incorporating feedback to improve project outcomes</li></ul>",
